  "text": "Other works like [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] and 10] also focus on the ANN method to adjust the input network parameters to get the ideal output to obtain the users' satisfaction. Principally, the success of the ANN approach depends on the model's capacity to completely learn the nonlinear interactions between QoE and QoS.",
